$(document).ready(function(){var t=$("#tickets").DataTable({rowId:"id",lengthChange:!1,ajax:"/tickets",columns:[{data:"id"},{data:"name"},{data:"created"},{data:"updated"},{data:"priority"},{data:"status"},{data:"project_name"},{data:"edit"}],initComplete:function(a,e){$("#tickets tfoot th").each(function(a){if("Priority"==$(this).text()||"Status"==$(this).text()||"Project"==$(this).text()){var e=$('<select><option value=""></option></select>').appendTo($(this).empty()).on("change",function(){t.column(a).search($(this).val()).draw()});t.column(a).data().unique().sort().each(function(t,a){e.append('<option value="'+t+'">'+t+"</option>")})}})},select:!1,searching:!0});$("#editTicket").on("hidden.bs.modal",function(t){$(this).removeData("bs.modal")})});